<html
  xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml'
  xmlns:v='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml'
  xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office'
>

  <head>
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <meta http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' />
    <link
      href='https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/calibri-light'
      rel='stylesheet'
    />
    <style type='text/css'>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; } html { display: flex; justify-content:
      center; flex-direction: column; margin: 0; padding: 0; align-items:
      center; } body { margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction:
      column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; align-content:
      center; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      font-family: "Calibri Light", sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight:
      500; line-height: 20px; text-align: start; } .body-container{ display:
      flex; justify-content: center; align-content: center; margin: auto; }
      .container { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-content:
      center; margin: auto; padding: 20px; } .standard-text { font-family:
      "Calibri Light", sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 20px; text-align: start; } .mt15 { margin-bottom: 15px; }
      .mb15 { margin-bottom: 15px; } .text-grey { font-weight: 900; color:
      #3d3d3d; } .text-blue { font-weight: 900; color: #0231a8; }
      .email-container { width: 600px; display: block; justify-content: start;
      align-items: start; justify-self: start; margin-top: 100px; background:
      #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; } .email-content { margin-top: 20px; } .greeting {
      display: block; justify-content: start; } .label { font-weight: 900; }
      .step { margin-left: 40px; } .email-footer { display: block; justify-self:
      start; line-height: 20px; } .fs10 { font-size: 10px; } @media screen and
      (max-width: 780px) { .container { margin: auto; display: flex;
      justify-content: center; align-content: center; padding: 5px; }
      .email-container { width: 600px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: start; align-items: start; justify-self: start;
      margin-top: 0px; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; } }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class='body-container'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='email-container'>
        <div class='logo'>
          <img
            src='https://i.imgur.com/XMv5crO.png'
            width='150px'
            alt='Ic Logo'
          />
        </div>
        <div class='email-content'>
          <div class='greeting mb15'>
            <p class='standard-text'>
              Veuillez cliquer sur le lien ci-dessous pour lancer la procédure
              de réinitialisation du mot de passe de votre compte IC :
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class='title-step label mb15'>
            <a href='{{linkToSummary}}'>{{linkToSummary}}</a>
          </div>

          <p class='mb15'>
            Veuillez noter que ce lien ne sera actif que pendant 60 minutes à
            compter de la date à laquelle il a été demandé.
          </p>

          <p class='mb15'>Bien cordialement,</p>
          <div class='email-footer mb15'>
            <p class='text-blue'>Innovation Campus</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>